requirements*.txt          @ndspence
.github/                   @ndspence

# Documentation
*.md                       @ndspence
/docs/                     @ndspence

# Tests - require review from maintainers
/tests/                    @ndspence

# CI/CD workflows
/.github/workflows/        @ndspence

# Security-sensitive files
/.github/SECURITY.md       @ndspence
/CODEOWNERS               @ndspence
